## [1.16.73-alpha] - 2026-06-07

### Sprint 35a freeze â Pre-freeze hardening (OricForge review)

Suite Ã  la revue OricForge sur le protocole 35a (mail 2026-06-07).
4 items ÂŦ Ã  acter avant freeze Âŧ livrÃĐs.

#### Added

- **`hello` handshake** : reply
