## [1.16.44-alpha] - 2026-06-07

### Sprint 34ar â Review ingÃĐ sÃĐnior : 3 fixes + cleanup compensations

Suite Ã  la review de l'ingÃĐ sÃĐnior (doc `docs/CR/2026-06-07_Senior_Review...`)
