  - `test_6502_initial_jsr_returns_zero` : prÃĐ-op, retourne 0/0
  - `test_6502_jsr_spin_zxstack_op_00` : op `0x00` efface xstack + retour 0
  - `test_6502_jsr_spin_returns_via_released_stub` : op RNG_LRAND,
    31-bit positif, BUSY clear, PC Ã  BRK sentinel
- `test_init_zeroes_state` mis Ã  jour pour le released no-op seedÃĐ
